Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.12,White,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.32,White,,0,0,0,,Candy, espera! Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:40.20,White,,0,0,0,,(vehicle: s'engega)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:48.96,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Espera, on vas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.40,White,,0,0,0,,Candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"D'amor i de crims sempre n'hi ha:\Nes repeteixen cada dia."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:04.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Una furgoneta de repartiment porta\Nuna bomba de rellotgeria."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:07.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Comença el compte enrere\Nper la Lliga de Detectius Júnior."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:15.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Take me to the high,\NWe never cry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mada mienai asu he.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:22.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Try again, try again,\Ntry again always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Try again, try again, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:28.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aru ga mama ni Speak Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:34.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:37.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nani wo mezasu no ka shiranai mama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:41.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Gamushara ni ima wo susumu way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:44.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sukoshi demo ue wo muite inai to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Fuan ni oshi tsubusare chau.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:51.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Anata wa kitto yume wo miru deshou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:54.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kanaetakute nakitakute\Ndemo oikakete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:58.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Anata wa sotto akirame chau no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Too sugita genjitsu imanara\Ncan't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Take me to the high,\NWe never cry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mada mienai asu he.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:13.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Try again, try again,\Ntry again always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Try again, try again, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:23.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Iya na koto bakari janai yo\Nbokura wa yume wo mite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:27.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Try again, try again,\Ntry again always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Try again, try again, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aru ga mama ni speak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:45.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La furgoneta que porta\Nuna bomba de rellotgeria."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.56,White,,0,0,0,,A quina hora tanca, la biblioteca\Nde Beika? Hi arribaríem a temps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Mao) Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.44,White,,0,0,0,,La Candy està en perill!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.00,White,,0,0,0,,Però, Mao, què ha passat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.00,White,,0,0,0,,-És la Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Qui és, aquesta nena?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.64,White,,0,0,0,,Si no vaig equivocat,\Nés una veïna de l'Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.24,White,,0,0,0,,La Candy s'ha ficat a la furgoneta\Nde repartiment que se n'ha anat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:10.56,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, Ayumi, i ara no sé què puc fer per trobar-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.56,White,,0,0,0,,No pateixis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.88,White,,0,0,0,,Nosaltres, els membres de la Lliga\Nde Detectius Júnior, la trobarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.08,White,,0,0,0,,Tranquil·la, la salvarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, anem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Som-hi, Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ei, aquest no és un cas\Nper la Lliga de Detectius.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:27.92,White,,0,0,0,,Tenim feina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.08,White,,0,0,0,,Mireu, no és aquella furgoneta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, té el dibuix de la guineu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho és?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.24,White,,0,0,0,,Són els missatgers FOX.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy, ets aquí? On t'has ficat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.04,White,,0,0,0,,Vinga, amunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy, on ets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Què passa, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Nois, què feu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.16,White,,0,0,0,,Hola, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Agent Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.16,White,,0,0,0,,No hi és.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.12,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors, deu ser\Nen una altra furgoneta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,-No pateixis, la trobarem ben aviat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:16.52,White,,0,0,0,,Nosaltres, la Lliga de Detectius Júnior, t'ajudarem, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.20,White,,0,0,0,,-I tant que sí, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Compta amb nosaltres!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.92,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per cert, agent Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Que ha passat alguna cosa, potser?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.72,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Doncs... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.48,White,,0,0,0,,(Takagi) Eh, Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.00,White,,0,0,0,,Allà no hi ha res. Aquí tampoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ah. Co... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.00,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Esteu treballant en un cas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.08,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, més o menys. Escolta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.76,White,,0,0,0,,Això és perillós per la canalla,\Nval més que aneu cap a casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:49.08,White,,0,0,0,,M'acaben de dir que n'han aturat\Nuna al sector 3. Anem-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.52,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Adeu. Bon dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Ens en anem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.12,White,,0,0,0,,Aquí en passa alguna...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Nois, espereu-me aquí\Nun moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Ai, tu també te'n vas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Espera, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.00,White,,0,0,0,,Quina barra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Daixò... Hola. Ets tu, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.40,Cyan,,0,0,0,,"Digui?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí. Que passa res, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Escolta, què està fent, ara,\Nel teu pare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.64,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ho vaig a mirar, espera un segon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.76,White,,0,0,0,,Au, va... Una copa més.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No pot ser... Què has fet, pare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sisplau...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "He-he-he.\NJa m'ho imaginava."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:30.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No t'amoïnis, Ran, no era res important. Ja ens veurem. Adeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, digui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.52,White,,0,0,0,,(telèfon)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.84,Green,,0,0,0,,Ah, ets tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.84,White,,0,0,0,,"Inspector, soc en Mouri."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Escolta,\Nara estic una mica enfeinat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.72,White,,0,0,0,,"Amb el cas d'una furgoneta\Nde repartiment?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.68,Green,,0,0,0,,Què dius? Qui t'ho ha explicat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.84,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) Per casualitat he vist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.92,White,,0,0,0,,l'inspector Takagi\Ni en Chiba investigant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.16,White,,0,0,0,,De quina mena de cas es tracta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.16,Green,,0,0,0,,"Ja ho entenc."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.28,Green,,0,0,0,,Mira, no puc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.08,White,,0,0,0,,"Si puc ajudar en alguna cosa,\Nsisplau, faci-m'ho saber."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.16,White,,0,0,0,,"Inspector?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:04.24,Green,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Mouri,\Nla veritat és aquest migdia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:06.44,Green,,0,0,0,,hi ha hagut dues explosions seguides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.68,White,,0,0,0,,Què? De debò?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La primera víctima,\Nen Kozo Tonomura,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,és jutge\Nd'un tribunal de districte."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La segona ha estat\Nen Kazuhiko Saeki, fiscal."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Totes dues víctimes han patit\Nferides greus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,però les seves vides\Nno corren perill."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En tots dos casos han rebut un paquet d'un servei de missatgeria."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Gràcies a les empremtes dactilars
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,trobades a les restes\Nde la primera bomba,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"s'ha pogut identificar l'autor,\Nun home anomenat Masato Utsugi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que fins fa un mes complia\Ncondemna a la presó."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Se l'ha detingut per violació\Nde la llei de control d'explosius."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:45.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Pretenia venjar-se dels que l'havien acusat i condemnat."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'Utsugi ha declarat\Nque ha enviat una tercera bomba
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,a un policia que l'havia detingut\Nen una ocasió anterior."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:58.00,White,,0,0,0,,Ja ho entenc. Per això revisen\Nles furgonetes de repartiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.04,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí, però resulta\Nque hi ha un problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.60,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.96,White,,0,0,0,,Hem confirmat que l'exinspector Kaneko està sa i estalvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.60,White,,0,0,0,,Pel que sembla,\Nla bomba encara no li ha arribat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.24,Green,,0,0,0,,Molt bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,Si fem cas\Ndel que ha dit en Masato Utsugi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.44,White,,0,0,0,,està previst que la bomba esclati\Na les 4 de la tarda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.36,Green,,0,0,0,,Encara ens queda una hora i mitja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.44,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Ens acaba de contestar\Nl'empresa de missatgeria FOX.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.48,White,,0,0,0,,Segons consta\Nen el registre d'enviaments,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.08,White,,0,0,0,,el lliurament està previst per avui
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.36,White,,0,0,0,,entre les 3 i les 4 de la tarda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.72,Green,,0,0,0,,I se sap on és, ara, la bomba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.68,White,,0,0,0,,L'empresa està intentant contactar\Namb la furgoneta de repartiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.64,White,,0,0,0,,Hem demanat a la brigada d'explosius\Nque estigui en alerta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.80,White,,0,0,0,,Quan la localitzem, aniran cap allà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:45.24,Green,,0,0,0,,Entesos. Espero que hi puguem arribar a temps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.72,White,,0,0,0,,(telèfon)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, digui?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.72,White,,0,0,0,,Però com és possible?\NQue han robat la furgoneta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.56,Green,,0,0,0,,Què dius?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.64,White,,0,0,0,,Soc la furgoneta número 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.96,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Una bom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Ei, què fas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Dona'm la clau, vinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.96,White,,0,0,0,,(Takagi) Kingo Ebisawa, de 28 anys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ginji Kaniyama, de 25 anys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.96,White,,0,0,0,,Tots dos tenen\Nantecedents per robatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.08,White,,0,0,0,,Avui, poc abans del migdia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.40,White,,0,0,0,,han entrat a Préstecs Marukane\Ni s'han endut un milió de iens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.52,White,,0,0,0,,Les imatges de la càmera de seguretat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.24,White,,0,0,0,,i la descripció que n'ha fet\Nel conductor coincideixen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:34.32,Green,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Préstecs Marukane...\NQue no era...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, és d'aquell usurer corrupte\Nde Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Però per què han robat\Nla furgoneta de repartiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.28,White,,0,0,0,,Pel que sembla, el cotxe\Namb què fugien s'havia espatllat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.36,White,,0,0,0,,L'han trobat abandonat allà a prop,\Namb les claus posades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.88,White,,0,0,0,,Potser ho han fet per interceptar\Nla ràdio de la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.56,White,,0,0,0,,Curiosament, al cotxe que han abandonat també hi havia una ràdio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.56,Green,,0,0,0,,Esclar, per això han robat\Nla furgoneta,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.36,Green,,0,0,0,,per tenir accés a la ràdio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:03.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, i és probable que no sàpiguen\Nque hi ha una bomba a dins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Oh. Ja és mala sort, això!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Estem fent tot el que podem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Tot i això, encara continuem\Nsense saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.00,Green,,0,0,0,,on es troba\Nla furgoneta de repartiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.00,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos. Per cert, on l'han robada,\Nla furgoneta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.44,Green,,0,0,0,,"Doncs... a la zona 3\Ndel districte de Beika."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.60,White,,0,0,0,,Molt bé, d'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.16,White,,0,0,0,,Si descobreixo alguna cosa\Nrelacionada amb el cas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.92,White,,0,0,0,,l'avisaré de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.84,White,,0,0,0,,A reveure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.84,Green,,0,0,0,,"Gràcies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.20,White,,0,0,0,,No em diguis\Nque és aquella furgoneta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Sí, Ai,\Nés molt probable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.20,White,,0,0,0,,Eh, Conan! Quanta estona més\Nens haurem d'esperar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.64,White,,0,0,0,,Al final, vols\Nque anem a buscar la Candy o no?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sisplau, l'hem d'ajudar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Tranquils,\Nesclar que la buscarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.72,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Mao, on era, la furgoneta,\Nquan hi ha pujat la Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.24,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.56,White,,0,0,0,,(ràdio: home) "Central de policia\Na totes les unitats."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.48,White,,0,0,0,,"Investigueu per la zona on\Ns'ha trobat el cotxe dels lladres."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ho hem aconseguit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.44,White,,0,0,0,,Així podrem enganyar la policia\Ni fugir sense problemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:09.16,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, Ginji. Ens ha anat molt bé\Nque siguis tan bon mecànic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.64,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Què hi fas, tu, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(Candy: borda)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Ha-ha-ha! Que bufó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Compte...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.56,White,,0,0,0,,(Mao) Aquí! Aquí és on la Candy\Nha pujat a la furgoneta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:27.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Llavors ha girat de seguida\Ni l'has perdut de vista, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.00,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:33.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Escolteu, de què serveix haver tornat aquí una altra vegada?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.56,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que a hores d'ara\Nla furgoneta ja deu ser lluny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:40.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Ai) Almenys ens podem fer una idea\Nde cap a on pot haver anat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.72,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? De debò?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,A la dreta hi ha\Nun carrer contra direcció.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,El de l'esquerra està en obres\Ni no s'hi pot passar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,La resta de carrerons laterals
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,són massa estrets\Nperquè hi passi una furgoneta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.88,White,,0,0,0,,Que ha d'haver anat recte avall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:00.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Molt bé! Correm, de pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:00.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Exacte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.68,White,,0,0,0,,(cotxe: botzina)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.36,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Que bé! Els cotxes estan aturats en un embús.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.92,White,,0,0,0,,Potser encara podrem trobar\Nla furgoneta i tot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, cap on... deu haver girat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.36,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) A la dreta? A l'esquerra?\NCap on hem d'anar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "Si tenim en compte l'estat\Npsicològic dels fugitius,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:22.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"és poc probable\Nque decidissin travessar l'embús
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,per anar cap a l'altra banda..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.88,White,,0,0,0,,Cap aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.80,White,,0,0,0,,-De pressa, de pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Sisplau, no corris tant, Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Tens raó, Ai. Per si de cas..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hola. Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:46.08,White,,0,0,0,,Punyeta! No hi ha alguna manera\Nde sortir d'aquest embús? Au, vinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:50.04,White,,0,0,0,,Ei, Kingo, et podries aturar\Nen un supermercat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.68,White,,0,0,0,,El gos i jo tenim molta gana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.52,White,,0,0,0,,Es pot saber què carai li passa?\NAixò no va!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.72,White,,0,0,0,,No sabia que enviessin gossos\Nper missatgeria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,Però s'han descuidat\Nde posar-hi l'adreça.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,On t'envien, eh?\NHe-he-he! Era una broma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.64,White,,0,0,0,,Vols parar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.00,White,,0,0,0,,I fes alguna cosa amb\Naquest navegador, que no funciona!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:16.04,White,,0,0,0,,Saps que aquest trasto podria ajudar la policia a trobar-nos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.68,White,,0,0,0,,Fins i tot els hi podria dir\Non som ara mateix.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.20,White,,0,0,0,,Vols dir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.64,White,,0,0,0,,Crec que ho vaig veure\Nen una pel·lícula o així...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.08,White,,0,0,0,,Per això quan hem pujat\Nl'he desconnectat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.64,White,,0,0,0,,Ah. Caram! Ben pensat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja els veig!\NSón a 300 metres d'aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.52,White,,0,0,0,,-No se'ns escaparan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Així ja els tenim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.40,White,,0,0,0,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.92,White,,0,0,0,,-No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.92,White,,0,0,0,,-Se'n van!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Ara que gairebé els havíem atrapat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Quina ràbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.28,White,,0,0,0,,-No els veig!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja gairebé els teníem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.80,White,,0,0,0,,-(cotxe: botzina)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Mao, et trobes bé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Doctor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Sento arribar tard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Afanyi's, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.00,White,,0,0,0,,Vostè sempre tan oportú!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.80,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.60,White,,0,0,0,,Cap on... he de tirar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.48,White,,0,0,0,,-On deuen haver anat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquí no hi són.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.36,White,,0,0,0,,És possible\Nque hagin agafat un altre carreró.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.84,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.00,White,,0,0,0,,Si és així,\Nserà impossible trobar-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ara què fem? Està previst\Nque esclati a les 4, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.48,White,,0,0,0,,Només ens queden 40 minuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Una bomba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:10.12,White,,0,0,0,,Oh, vaja. Ells no en sabien res, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:10.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja ho ha dit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.32,White,,0,0,0,,Què vol dir, amb això?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.76,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que ara\Nels hi haurem d'explicar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí. Resulta que...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.48,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Una bomba de rellotgeria esclatarà a les 4?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.12,White,,0,0,0,,Candy! Què li passarà a la Candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.36,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres! I què ha estat fent,\Nla policia, fins ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.08,White,,0,0,0,,Si tenen la matrícula,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.56,White,,0,0,0,,per què no els empaiten,\No tallen els carrers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.36,White,,0,0,0,,I la ràdio, què?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.68,White,,0,0,0,,¿Per què no intenten contactar\Namb ells
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.84,White,,0,0,0,,i dir-los que és perillós,\Nque hi ha una bomba a la furgoneta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:41.08,White,,0,0,0,,Estic segura\Nque estan fent el que poden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.20,White,,0,0,0,,La veritat és que deu ser\Nmolt difícil saber exactament
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.84,White,,0,0,0,,quina de les moltes furgonetes\Nde la missatgeria FOX
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.76,White,,0,0,0,,que volten per la ciutat\Nés la que porta la bomba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:54.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,A més, sembla que els fugitius escoltaven la ràdio de la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si munten un control\No contacten amb ells per ràdio,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,podrien abandonar la furgoneta\Ni encara seria pitjor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:04.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy... Candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:04.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Què hem de fer, llavors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.92,White,,0,0,0,,Perdona que t'hagi fet esperar,\Ngosset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.28,White,,0,0,0,,-El podem agafar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh! Que bufó!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.96,White,,0,0,0,,Què, gosset? Vols anar amb ells?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.76,White,,0,0,0,,Eh, Ginji, anem o què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.96,White,,0,0,0,,Au, va, una estoneta més.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sí! Ja ho tinc!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Surto un moment,\Nvosaltres espereu-me aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Doctor, estigui a punt\Nperquè puguem sortir de seguida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Però, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Entesos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Què penses fer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.48,White,,0,0,0,,Soc en Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.48,Green,,0,0,0,,"Inspector Megure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.08,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector, si no recordo malament,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.24,White,,0,0,0,,ha dit que els delinqüents tenien accés a la ràdio de la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.96,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí, creiem que és el més probable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:02.08,White,,0,0,0,,En aquest cas, li demano que faci\Nexactament el que ara li diré.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.08,Green,,0,0,0,,T'escolto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:08.04,Green,,0,0,0,,N'estàs segur?\NPerò... però això que dius...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.60,Green,,0,0,0,,D'acord, entesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Poseu-me amb el centre de control\Nde comunicacions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.24,Green,,0,0,0,,I també amb en Takagi i en Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.72,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos, inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.60,White,,0,0,0,,De debò sou de la missatgeria FOX,\Nvosaltres dos?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:34.20,White,,0,0,0,,Com és que no porteu l'uniforme?\NAquell amb la guineu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.56,White,,0,0,0,,Ginji, vinga, anem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:43.36,White,,0,0,0,,Ets un desastre! Si aquells nanos avisen la policia, veuràs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.76,White,,0,0,0,,Kingo, escolta, corrent així,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.64,White,,0,0,0,,després no t'estranyis\Nque t'aturin per excés de velocitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:52.36,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Sí, esclar... Tens tota la raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.80,White,,0,0,0,,(ràdio: home) "Centre de control\Na totes les unitats."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:59.28,White,,0,0,0,,"Estableixin punts de control\Na les zones següents:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,de la intersecció de la ruta circular interior 3 de Kurinishi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí! El mapa! El mapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho has sentit, Kingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.36,White,,0,0,0,,"Repeteixo, estableixin\Npunts de control..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.12,White,,0,0,0,,Uf, això no pinta bé! Per aquí\Nanirem a petar a un control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.20,White,,0,0,0,,Què? Punyeta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.80,White,,0,0,0,,"...a la intersecció\Nde Tanmondai Mae."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:19.40,White,,0,0,0,,Si... si vas cap allà,\Net trobaràs un altre control!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.00,White,,0,0,0,,(Kingo) Avisa'm amb més temps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:26.28,White,,0,0,0,,(Ginji) Ves cap aquí.\NDesprés a l'esquerra i a la dreta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.24,White,,0,0,0,,La que ve a la dreta.\NNo, a l'esquerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.44,White,,0,0,0,,-La següent, la següent a l'esquerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Aclareix-te!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Kingo) D'acord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.28,White,,0,0,0,,(Ginji) Ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.88,White,,0,0,0,,Al final ho hem aconseguit!\NHem evitat els controls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.56,White,,0,0,0,,Visca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.48,White,,0,0,0,,-És aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.28,White,,0,0,0,,-No esperava menys de tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja els tenim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.04,White,,0,0,0,,Com t'ho has fet, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:05.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Li he dit al senyor Kogoro\Nque li demanés a l'inspector Megure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que donés informació falsa\Nsobre els controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.04,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, esclar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:11.92,White,,0,0,0,,Has fet veure que l'única sortida era aquest carrer secundari
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.80,White,,0,0,0,,i els has dirigit fins aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Justa la fusta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:19.48,White,,0,0,0,,(megafonia: Chiba) "Furgoneta\Nde la missatgeria FOX, aturi's!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.88,White,,0,0,0,,(Ginji) Ha-ha-ha! Tinguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Compte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.60,White,,0,0,0,,A reveure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.52,White,,0,0,0,,No... no hi és. No hi és!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.32,White,,0,0,0,,No hi és, no hi és...\NLa bomba encara és a la furgoneta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Obri el portaequipatge, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.68,White,,0,0,0,,De pressa!\NNomés queden 12 minuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aquest no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aquí tampoc hi és.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hola! Tu deus ser la Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.96,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ei!\NTu, nano, es pot saber què fas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja la tinc!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ostres, queda molt poc temps."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però no la puc llençar\Nen un lloc habitat."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Escoltin amb molta atenció!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,M'han de portar de seguida a\Nun espai obert on no hi hagi gent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.40,White,,0,0,0,,Què? Una bomba!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això és una bomba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.20,White,,0,0,0,,(Kingo) I què més, home! Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.56,White,,0,0,0,,-D'acord, Kingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Va, fes-lo fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És la veritat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aquesta furgoneta ja ha repartit dues bombes, i hi ha hagut ferits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:33.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Encara queda aquesta,\Ni falta molt poc perquè esclati!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:48.04,White,,0,0,0,,Nano, agafa't fort on puguis!\NGinji, el mapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.92,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, de seguida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.64,White,,0,0,0,,No hi ha cap espai obert,\Ncap ni un que estigui a prop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.24,White,,0,0,0,,Falten dos minuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,A veure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.48,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ja ho sé! On són? On s'han ficat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.08,White,,0,0,0,,Són allà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vagi cap allà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:12.28,White,,0,0,0,,Merda! On dimoni han anat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:15.48,White,,0,0,0,,Només falta un minut!\NS'acaba el temps!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.32,White,,0,0,0,,No et rendeixis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.68,White,,0,0,0,,-On són?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Falten 20 segons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.64,White,,0,0,0,,Falten 10 segons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.84,White,,0,0,0,,Són allà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.64,White,,0,0,0,,Tres, dos, un...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja és massa tard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.60,White,,0,0,0,,-No pot ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.96,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.08,White,,0,0,0,,Quina sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:51.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Uf! Ha anat de ben poc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.20,White,,0,0,0,,Para, no em llepis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.60,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, mira que és maca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.16,White,,0,0,0,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.28,White,,0,0,0,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.88,White,,0,0,0,,La Lliga de Detectius Júnior\Nho ha tornat a aconseguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:13.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Secret love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Secret love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:20.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi ni zenzen kyoumi nai,\Nuso you are my perfect guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tokimeki wa kakusenai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Honto wa ki ni natte shikanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:29.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Koi ni bukiyou sokona style\NKimi no mae da to betsujin mitai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Dare ni mo ienai himitsu no mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Soredemo I'm alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:43.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Koi no yukue nante.\NMada it isn't the last chance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:48.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ironna love story wo\Negaiteru mune no naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:56.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Demo risou ni wa hodo tooi\Nwatashitte wagamama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:05.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sore kurai no koto wakatteru.\NDakedo nani ka ikenai no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:15.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to no koi ni koi wo shiteru dake de tsutaetakutemo mada.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:20.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Himitsu ni shiteru\Nhou ga shiawase dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:26.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,ima wa watashi dake no\Nsecret love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.48,Green,,0,0,0,,"Mouri, has estat fantàstic,\Ncom era d'esperar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.60,White,,0,0,0,,Sí! Com era d'esperar,\Nja no puc beure més!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:41.04,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare! A veure\Nsi t'aixeques d'una vegada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:43.24,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:50.96,White,,0,0,0,,Es va matar l'any passat\Nen un accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.88,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, que bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:57.36,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.64,White,,0,0,0,,Aquell dia el pare em va dir\Nque el venia a veure a vostè.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:02.96,White,,0,0,0,,Estic tip de dir\Nque no el vaig veure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:07.00,White,,0,0,0,,És que aquesta nit l'he vist...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:09.56,White,,0,0,0,,El fantasma de l'alcalde.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:14.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:\N"La misteriosa trampa de gel".
